{"tid":2155682,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"鄭敬基：以黎智英為榮","createTime":"2020-08-14T03:03:11.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-14T03:03:11.000Z","uid":25558,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"09d5315ba84f33875c10c08a823efd6823625847","tid":2155682,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-14T03:03:11.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/entertainment/20200814/QXIW6NAP3JGUXDXREOTHZL5CSA/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fentertainment%2F20200814%2FQXIW6NAP3JGUXDXREOTHZL5CSA%2F&d=Bi55TGPCxKeiDoZ%2FBZgBR%2BSCO5RJLUOM1IbOSdmZk8c%3D&h=ddcdfe46\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fentertainment%2F20200814%2FQXIW6NAP3JGUXDXREOTHZL5CSA%2F&h=2678a0f1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/entertainment/20200814/QXIW6NAP3JGUXDXREOTHZL5CSA/</a><br />\n<br />\n節錄<br />\n<br />\n鄭敬基：以黎智英為榮<br />\n<br />\n。。。。。。。。。。現身在加拿大的鄭敬基前晚在fb中開live撐《蘋果日報》：「作為報紙老闆，其實有好多option（選擇）可以做，但佢一直冇摒棄香港人，黎生話要留守到最後，煮到嚟就食，黎智英先生，世界上有好多香港人都以你為榮！」他又提議。。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/JfiBN1-fN6EZY-OQaVXWJG_wFyw=/640x900/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/DRILWJA7OJAFNOS4Y4PZZ22FPI.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FJfiBN1-fN6EZY-OQaVXWJG_wFyw%3D%2F640x900%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FDRILWJA7OJAFNOS4Y4PZZ22FPI.jpg&h=71e85da7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■鄭敬基前晚開直播撐《蘋果日報》，呼籲加國港人為公義發聲。互聯網圖片<br />\n<br />\n。。。。。。。。。：「我爸爸向黎先生要求錄製《給Donald Trump的信》，黎先生一口就答應了（在未知道我爸計劃甚麼內容之前）&hellip;&hellip;影片和新聞推出，得到很大迴響，超過100萬點擊，傳到班農（Steve Bannon）處，應該等於傳到美國總統處了。。。。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/U92ojJ9bttPjz3bajSErRrGF0cQ=/640x480/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/H4JC6VO33NE3FKSBRYAGPCH5AY.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FU92ojJ9bttPjz3bajSErRrGF0cQ%3D%2F640x480%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FH4JC6VO33NE3FKSBRYAGPCH5AY.jpg&h=fb1bfa6f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■袁彌明於fb撰寫千字文撐黎智英，亦支持父親袁弓夷華盛頓之行。資料圖片"}]}